WEBVTT

00:00.061 --> 00:01.115
<i>Previously on "Suits"...</i>

00:01.116 --> 00:03.772
As of this morning,
we're merging with Robert Zane.

00:03.798 --> 00:05.262
When I came over,
you said my name

00:05.263 --> 00:06.451
would be the one to go up next.

00:06.452 --> 00:08.439
You have my word.
Your name goes up next.

00:08.440 --> 00:10.267
I threw away my diaphragm.

00:10.268 --> 00:13.179
- You're pulling the goalie?
- Yes, Louis, I am.

00:13.180 --> 00:15.480
I need you to get
Robert Zane's biggest client

00:15.516 --> 00:16.957
to sell their
manufacturing division.

00:16.984 --> 00:19.451
This is going to determine
who runs the firm.

00:19.486 --> 00:21.031
I need you to come through
for me on this one.

00:21.055 --> 00:24.289
Your client is dropping
their manufacturing division,

00:24.325 --> 00:25.835
and we can get back to the
business of running this firm

00:25.859 --> 00:27.526
under the direction
of Robert Zane.

00:27.561 --> 00:29.161
You think I can't take
Samantha Wheeler?

00:29.196 --> 00:30.823
I think you said
you'd stay out of it,

00:30.824 --> 00:32.764
and I'm not going to help you
tell your own team

00:32.765 --> 00:33.743
that you'll cut them out

00:33.744 --> 00:35.576
just to get the better
of Samantha Wheeler.

00:35.612 --> 00:38.012
I did what you asked, and
now I have something to ask.

00:38.048 --> 00:39.647
- What's that?
- You know what I want.

00:39.683 --> 00:41.549
- Samantha.
- Robert, I want name partner,

00:41.584 --> 00:43.351
and I want it
before the year is out.

00:43.386 --> 00:44.819
You said
that I should come back

00:44.854 --> 00:46.654
when I was ready to admit
that you were right.

00:46.690 --> 00:49.257
Takes a big man
to admit that, Harvey.

00:49.292 --> 00:50.758
- My office.
- What about it?

00:50.794 --> 00:52.660
- I want it back.
- Your fearless leader

00:52.696 --> 00:55.129
is happy to comply.

